summary: ...NOAA AND AIR FORCE HURRICANE HUNTERS INVESTIGATING JERRY... As of 8:00 AM AST Thu Oct 09 the center of Jerry was located near 15.7, -58.4 with movement WNW at 20 mph. The minimum central pressure was 999 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 65 mph.
